FAQ_TITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Sweet Talk: Your Candy Questions Answered
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Unwrap the mysteries of our sugary app and satisfy your curiosity
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of sweets does your app feature?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app covers a wide range of sweets, including chocolates, gummies, hard candies, lollipops, and more. We're constantly updating our selection to bring you the latest and greatest in the world of confectionery.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How does the sweet recommendation feature work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Our sweet recommendation engine uses your taste preferences, past purchases, and browsing history to suggest candies you're likely to love. The more you use the app, the more personalized your recommendations become!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I track my candy consumption using the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Our app includes a candy journal feature where you can log your sweet treats, set consumption goals, and even receive reminders to indulge in moderation.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Are there any sugar-free options available?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, we offer a variety of sugar-free and low-sugar alternatives. You can easily filter your search results to show only sugar-free options, perfect for those watching their sugar intake or with dietary restrictions.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How often are new sweets added to the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We update our sweet selection weekly, introducing new candies, limited edition flavors, and seasonal treats. Be sure to check the 'What's New' section regularly to stay up-to-date with the latest sugary sensations!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What types of sweets does your app feature?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app showcases a wide variety of sweets, including chocolates, candies, pastries, cakes, and regional specialties from around the world. We're constantly updating our selection to satisfy every sweet tooth!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I order sweets through the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! Our app allows you to browse, select, and order your favorite sweets for delivery or pickup. We partner with local confectioneries and international brands to bring you the best sugary delights.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Are there any features for users with dietary restrictions?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, we cater to various dietary needs. You can filter sweets by categories such as vegan, gluten-free, sugar-free, and nut-free. Each product also includes detailed ingredient information to help you make informed choices.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Does the app offer any rewards or loyalty program?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Indeed! Our SweetRewards program lets you earn points on every purchase. These points can be redeemed for discounts, free treats, or exclusive access to limited-edition sweets. The more you indulge, the sweeter the rewards!
